Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:33.05,Insert - CN - 4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(1830,30)\alpha&H00&}在這風平浪靜的夜晚
Comment: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:26.65,Note,,0,0,0,,「瞬く日々へ」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:46.29,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}青く煌めく空の真ん中に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:49.55,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}ぽつりと白い言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:54.05,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}僕らだけの理由　僕らだけの未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:57.67,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}ただ描いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:05.80,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}「また明日たね」の繰り返しの中で心近づく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:10.25,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}楽しかったり　傷ついたり
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:14.99,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}不器用に歩くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:20.49,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}ぎゅと手を繋ぐ　言葉は届く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:23.27,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}優しく背を押す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:26.48,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}丸いポスト　横断歩道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:29.09,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}泣き顔も笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.42,Insert - JP - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}どれも愛しい…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.11,0:19:46.29,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}在湛藍天空的正中央
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.56,0:19:49.55,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}浮現出孤零零的白色話語
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.82,0:19:54.05,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}僅僅描繪著
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.43,0:19:57.67,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}只屬於我們的理由  只屬於我們的未來
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.13,0:20:05.80,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}在一次次的「明天見」中  彼此的心一點點靠近
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.01,0:20:10.25,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}時而歡笑  時而受傷
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.46,0:20:14.99,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}笨拙地向前進
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.47,0:20:20.49,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}緊緊握住手  傳達我的話語
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.76,0:20:23.27,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}你溫柔地推了推我的背
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.65,0:20:26.48,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}圓圓的信箱  斑馬線
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.48,0:20:29.09,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}不論是哭臉還是笑臉
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.42,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}都如此惹人憐愛…
